summary: ...LARGE SWELLS AFFECTING COAST OF WEST-CENTRAL MEXICO AND BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR... ...TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS POSSIBLE IN PORTIONS OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR LATER TODAY THROUGH WEDNESDAY... As of 2:00 PM MST Tue Oct 07 the center of Priscilla was located near 19.9, -110.8 with movement WNW at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 958 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 110 mph.
